These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, lemonade, tea
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, peach, plum, radish
4 different pets are kept: fish, hedgehog, frog, guinea-pig
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, australian, argentine, indian
4 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, bridge, mah-jongg
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, bongani, montecristo, baccarat
 1. the indian is on the far right##1
 2. the person drinking lemonade is the person playing backgammon##1
 3. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 4. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 5. the person drinking tea is the person eating radish##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 7. the argentine is between the bluemaster-smoker and the person playing mah-jongg##2
 8. the owner of the fish is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
 9. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the nigerian##1
10. the bluemaster-smoker is between the argentine and the person eating radish##2
11. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
12. the indian is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
13. the person playing bridge is between the person playing scrabble and the owner of the frog##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4      |
| Beverage      | tea        | coffee       | lemonade  | almond-milk |
| Food          | radish     | plum         | peach     | broccoli    |
| Pet         | hedgehog  | fish      | frog   | guinea-pig     |
| Nationality           | australian | nigerian | argentine   | indian     |
| Game   | scrabble    | bridge         | backgammon | mah-jongg         |
| Cigar         | baccarat     | bluemaster     | bongani  | montecristo       |

