.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, july, may, august
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, filmmaking, skydiving, writing
4 different games are played: chess, scrabble, bridge, domino
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, electronic, folk, gospel
4 different pets are kept: horse, rabbit, pony, fish
House: townhouse, farmhouse, art-deco, gothic-revival
 1. the owner of the rabbit is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the townhouse house##2
 2. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
 4. the owner of the rabbit is between the person who's birthday is in november and the art-deco house##2
 5. the fan of disco is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 6. the fan of folk is on the far right##1
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 8. the art-deco house is between the person playing chess and the person who's hobby is writing##2
 9. the person playing scrabble is the person who's hobby is writing##1
10. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left##1
11. the fan of disco is the person playing bridge##1
12. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
13. the owner of the pony is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
14. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Birthday      | august    | july       | may   | november |
| Hobby         | chess     | skydiving   | writing    | filmmaking  |
| Game   | chess    | bridge | scrabble   | domino     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | disco       | electronic | folk        |
| Pet   | fish | pony   | rabbit     | horse    |
| House     | farmhouse       | art-deco        | gothic-revival      | townhouse        |

