4 different games are played: backgammon, snooker, mah-jongg, billiard
 1. the egyptian is on the right of the person eating lime##1
 2. the paramedic is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
 3. the palace house is on the right of the scientist##1
 4. the person eating corn is on the left of the russian##1
 5. the farmhouse house is the person watching scientific movies##1
 6. the librarian is on the far right##1
 7. the person playing billiard is between the mexican and the person watching time-travel movies##2
 8. the person watching documentary movies is the designer##1
 9. the person watching comedy movies is between the person playing billiard and the scientist##2
10. the colonial house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
11. the person watching time-travel movies is the person playing mah-jongg##1
12. the person eating lime is the person playing snooker##1
13. the paramedic is between the person eating cauliflower and the egyptian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |       3       |    4     |
