4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, havana, vegafina, bongani
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, metal, electronic, r&b
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, family, scientific
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, purple, blood-red, ebony
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, subway, taxi
 1. the owner of the goat is between the havana-smoker and the person who likes blood-red##2
 2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the fan of metal##1
 3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
 4. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 5. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 6. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 7. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
 8. the person driving the subway is the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the person driving the car is between the fan of electronic and the old-henry-smoker##2
10. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
11. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the person driving the car##1
12. the fan of r&b is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
13. the owner of the hedgehog is the owner of the hedgehog##1
14. the vegafina-smoker is the person who likes apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |         2          |     3      |     4     |
| Pet      | rabbit        | goat              | hedgehog      | frog  |
| Cigar         | old-henry | bongani            | havana | vegafina |
